Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.66,0:00:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unknown are the names{\i0}\N{\i1}of the flowers that have been trampled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Birds have fallen to the earth{\i0}\N{\i1}and long for the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Prayers won't solve anything{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only the will to fight{\i0}\N{\i1}can change the here and now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O pigs who laugh at the resolve{\i0}\N{\i1}to walk over corpses to move forward{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Livestock complacency? False prosperity?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give us the freedom of dying,{\i0}\N{\i1}starving wolves!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The humiliation of being caged{\i0}\N{\i1}is what triggers us to fight back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.70,0:01:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We hunters slaughter prey{\i0}\N{\i1}beyond the castle walls,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}consumed with surging bloodlust,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as our crimson bows and arrows{\i0}\N{\i1}pierce scarlet holes into the twilight{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"A Dim Light Amid Despair"\N"Humanity's Comeback, Part 1"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.20,0:01:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.37,0:01:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:01:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.08,0:02:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin Arlelt, from Shiganshina District!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.29,0:02:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! That's a ridiculous name!\NDid your parents give it to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandfather did, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Arlelt! Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To help humanity achieve victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.33,0:02:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful to hear!\NWe can feed you to the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Third row, about face!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.83,0:02:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! Thomas Wagner, from Trost District!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--Thomas Wagner--\N--Can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--Look at them go.\N--Go practice in a barn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You went through the same thing\Nwhen you started as a cadet, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You're from a pigsty!\NYou're less than livestock!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir! I am less than livestock!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,--No!\N--But what's all that intimidation for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rite of passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We revert them to a blank slate\Nthrough the use of self-denial,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,after which we mold them into proper soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,--Change it at once! Why are you here?!\N--This is one step in that process.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To devote myself to humankind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Fourth row, about face!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:03:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some he's not talking to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unnecessary for those who've\Nalready been through their rites of passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They most likely witnessed the hell\Nthat took place two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They have a different look on their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean Kirschtein, from Trost District!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To join the Military Police Regiment\Nand live in the interior!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. You wanna live in the interior, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said you could sit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't handle {\i1}this{\i0},\Nyou can forget about the Military Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?! Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Marco Bodt of Jinae, on the south side of Wall Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to join the Military Police Regiment\Nand give life and limb to the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fine goal, indeed. Go ahead and strive for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But, just so you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:04:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The king doesn't {\i1}want {\i0}your lousy life or limbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're next! Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Conny Springer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Ragako Village\Non the south side of Wall Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You have it backwards, Conny Springer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first thing you were taught!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This salute expresses your resolve\Nto give your heart to the people!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your heart on your right side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking to {\i1}you{\i0}! Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasha Braus from Dauper Village,\Non the south side of Wall Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasha Braus...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that you're holding in your right hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A steamed potato, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:05:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I found one in the cookhouse\Nthat was ready to eat, so I couldn't help myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}stole {\i0}it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you decide to eat it {\i1}now{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt it would be a waste to let it get cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so I elected to eat it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why {\i0}did you eat the potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you asking me why people eat potatoes, Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's half of it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Half...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. He {\i1}still {\i0}has Potato Girl running.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, she's been at it for five solid hours.\NShe's really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:06:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, being told to run\Nuntil she's on the verge of death
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't seem to bother her quite as much\Nas being told she has to skip meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dauper's a small hunting village\Nin the mountains, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They're dropouts. They asked\Nto work in the fields instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. It's only the first day, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how it is. If you\Ncan't cut it here, you have to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe anyone would {\i1}want{\i0}\Nto pick up rocks and pull plants again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, we haven't heard\Nanything about where you're from.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Shiganshina, same as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You were there that day, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see the Colossal Titan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.79,0:06:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes{\i0}, I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How big is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:06:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough to look over the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! I heard it stepped {\i1}over {\i0}the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they said in my village too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't that big.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What did it look like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It had a huge mouth, and almost no skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the Armored Titan\Nthat broke Wall Maria?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what people call it, but it\Nlooked like an ordinary Titan to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then, what are ordinary Titans like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's spare him the questions, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there are things\Nhe doesn't want to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for asking--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Titans aren't actually that big of a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we've mastered omni-directional mobility gear,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll be nothing to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We {\i1}finally {\i0}get to train as soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just overcome with emotion, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to join the Scout Regiment\Nand drive the Titans out of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna slaughter them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, what are you, crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just say you're gonna join\Nthe Scout Regiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the one\Nwho wants to join the Military Police
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and live the easy life?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all about being honest, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's much nicer than being,\Nsay, a loser who acts tough
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but is actually scared shitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes no difference to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean to dismiss your ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm sorry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh, err, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just never seen anyone\Nwho looks like you before...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You have very pretty black hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no big deal. Get off my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You never think things through\Nwhen you get worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, don't you think your hair's too long?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It could cause an accident\Nduring ODM training, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But how short should I make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Don't mess with other people's clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you wipe on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My trust in others...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally... done...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Bread!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not much, but I saved it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You really ought to drink some water first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,--Are you God?!\N--Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,--Are you?!\N--Uhh--!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,God!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:11:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, she's been running\Nnon-stop all this time, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're trying to do something "nice," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do it for Potato Girl's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Was what you gained worth the effort it took?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just get her to her bed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to be nice, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this so that she'll owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Her stupidity will come in very handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll begin by determining your aptitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't do this, you're not even fit to be bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be sent off to the fields!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,These are only just the bare fundamentals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:12:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you can determine a person's knack\Nfor omni-mobility at this stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She knows exactly what to do and how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what aptitude is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we have many talented cadets this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, what about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.87,0:12:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now {\i1}that's {\i0}the very definition of aptitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people might have plenty of motivation...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...yet turn out to be less-than-capable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Eren Jaeger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Straighten yourself up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I work this thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be for real...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just follow the basics and you'll be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think about being fancy or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus on your front and back balance,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,then slowly place your weight\Ninto the belts on your waist and feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it if you stay calm.\NEven I did it, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I feel like I've got it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Lift me up, Armin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Daz.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he the one who said he was\Ngonna slaughter all the Titans yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's off to the fields for him tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we can't afford to feed the useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point worrying about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just learn to do it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can wipe them out like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You should just forget about that altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying you should give up trying to be a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting isn't about simply throwing your life away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now! I saw what happened that day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think\Nyou can just convince me to quit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it doesn't matter {\i1}how {\i0}determined you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because {\i1}you {\i0}don't get to decide\Nif you're fit to be a soldier or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,--I'm not saying you should return...\N--Let's go, Armin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,--...to the fields by yourself.\N--Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when you go, I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, umm... What you're saying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I can have that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The trick to posture control?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm gifted. All I can tell you is to "feel" it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, I'd like to hear {\i1}your {\i0}trick
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,for staying sane after\Nputting on such a pathetic spectacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, guys! I'm begging you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But didn't you say yesterday,\N"If you can't cut it here, you have to leave"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, wait. Was it, "If you don't got talent,\Nyou have to leave"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Which was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I heard you're both really good at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Bertholdt! Reiner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I don't think there {\i1}are{\i0}\Nany tricks to just hanging there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of any especially helpful advice, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll just have to hope for the best tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:16:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are, umm, from Shiganshina, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you {\i1}know {\i0}how terrifying the Titans are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So why do you want to be soldiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike Eren, I didn't witness\Nthe Titan threat firsthand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided I couldn't sit there\Nand do nothing after the royal government
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,forced people into\Nthat absolutely awful retrieval operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you two from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Reiner and I are from a mountain village
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,on the southeast side of Wall Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Wasn't that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike the prosperous towns along the river,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,we didn't receive word right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Titans showed up\Nwell before the information did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened at dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The livestock were acting up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and these strange rumblings\Nkept getting louder and louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:17:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,At some point, I realized\Nthey were footfalls of some sort...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, when I hurriedly opened the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,After that... I, umm, don't really remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was in such a panic...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now. What are you\Nsuddenly bringin' that up for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, what I was trying to say
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,is that you guys probably aren't like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Them"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The others here who don't know\Nthe horror of the Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They're mostly here for show;\Nto live up to society's expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're seen as a coward if you choose\Nproduction work when you turn twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Society has pushed them into becoming cadets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:18:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That said, I'm no different than them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose to be a soldier\Nin the hopes of joining the Military Police
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,so I could work in the safety of the interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If that doesn't work out, I might give up entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any will to call my own, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Cherishing your life {\i1}is {\i0}admirable too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to return to the hometown we lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I care about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}will {\i0}do it, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do {\i1}you {\i0}want to be a soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided I have to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.70,0:18:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided I have to slaughter all the Titans
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,with my own two hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, your encounter with the Titans\N{\i1}didn't {\i0}break your will?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But {\i1}now {\i0}it's a question of whether or not
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually cut out to be a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Start over from scratch,\Nstarting with your belt adjustment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll do just fine tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren Jaeger, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Reiner Braun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren Jaeger. Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do it! I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I might not have raw aptitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but no one has more guts than I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell with logic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's completely baseless!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But guts are all I got!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...my weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can still do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.95,0:21:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wagner. Switch belts with Jaeger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your equipment was defective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The belt you were using had a broken clasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of this part breaking before;
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll have to add it\Nto the maintenance checklist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.50,0:21:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, even with broken equipment,\Nhe still managed to...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then, am I fit to be a soldier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You pass muster. Train hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it! I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Whadya think of that, Mikasa?! I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can fight the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can finally stop mollycoddling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:22:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like things worked out for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes say, "What do you think of that?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.41,0:22:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He feels relieved that\Nhe doesn't have to leave me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.45,0:22:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Grisha...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, your son has become a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.91,0:23:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your dreams are where your heart is{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.83,0:23:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're more fragile than life itself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.08,0:23:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Over and over you cast them aside,{\i0}\N{\i1}only to find more{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.79,0:23:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, rest in peace{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pounding impulses defile the things we wish for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.58,0:23:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the more we forget{\i0}\N{\i1}the more we remember again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.12,0:23:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In this beautiful, cruel world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.08,0:23:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}all I can do is ask why we're still alive{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.37,0:23:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, with our strength--and our weakness--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.00,0:24:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}what are we going to protect if there's no sense{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.54,0:24:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to anything anymore?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.75,0:24:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,After graduating from the Cadets,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.45,0:24:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren sees humanity and its regained dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.37,0:24:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"We can beat the Titans."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.20,0:24:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment he feels certain of this,\Nhumanity is reminded yet again...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.20,0:24:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Night of the Closing Ceremony"\N"Humanity's Comeback, Part 2"
